      <h2>1. About Us</h2>
      <p>Hyche International Management ("we," "us," "our," or "the Agency") is a boutique athlete representation firm based in Jackson, Mississippi. This website provides information about our services and allows visitors to contact us regarding potential representation or brand partnerships.</p>

      <h2>2. Use of This Website</h2>
      <p>You may use this website for informational purposes, to learn about our services, and to contact us. You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the website for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any portion of the website or its systems</li>
