      <ul>
        <li>Legal advice</li>
        <li>Financial advice</li>
        <li>Tax advice</li>
        <li>A guarantee of any outcome or result</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Athletes, families, and brands should consult qualified legal, financial, and tax professionals before making decisions based on information found on this website.</p>

      <h2>5. Athlete Profiles and Content</h2>
      <p>Athletes featured on this website are represented by Hyche International Management under signed agreements. Their names, likenesses, statistics, and related content are displayed with their consent (or the consent of their parent or legal guardian, where applicable). Any use of this content by third parties requires express written permission.</p>

      <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
